# Public build-time config for the Vercel PRODUCTION build. Vite bakes VITE_*
# values in at `vite build`, so these must be present at build time (the Vercel
# dashboard env vars are the alternative and OVERRIDE this file if set).
#
# Both values are PUBLIC by design — the anon key ships in the browser bundle
# and is safe to commit. Real secrets (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, MPESA_*, service-role)
# live in Supabase Edge Function secrets and never appear here.
#
# Local dev uses .env (gitignored); this file only affects production builds.
